text: Aghamore is a village in County Leitrim, Ireland Aghamore may also refer to: ==Places== ;Northern Ireland *Aghamore, County Fermanagh, a townland in the civil parish of Inishmacsaint *Aghamore, County Tyrone, a townland in the civil parish of Termonamongan ;Republic of Ireland *Aghamore, Croghan, a townland in the barony of Lower Philipstown, County Offaly *Aghamore, Killucan, a townland in the barony of Farbill, County Westmeath *Aghamore, Kilbeggan, a townland in the barony of Moycashel, County Westmeath *Aghamore, Kilbride, a townland in the barony of Kilcoursey, County Offaly *Aghamore, County Mayo, a village and parish in County Mayo **Aghamore GAA, a Gaelic Athletic Association club in the parish of Aghamore, just outside Knock village in County Mayo
